  m_text: "You will follow Ainaz, a school student who slowly begins to notice\L
    that something is wrong with her friend, Guldana.\n\nThe game explores domestic
    violence \Lboth physical and psychological \u2014through situations that are
    not always easy to recognize.\n\nYour choices will affect trust, risk, and safety.\n\nThere
    are no completely right answers.\nOnly your path."
