  m_text: "\u201CWhen the Light Goes Out\u201D is an interactive story about choice,
    trust, and noticing the things that often remain unseen.\n\nThe story takes place
    in a small village near Bishkek.\n\nLife there seems quiet and ordinary.\nBut
    not everything is as it appears."
